flowchart TD
    A[Question from UI/CLI] --> B[Load DB Schema]
    B --> C[GuardrailsAgent.evaluate]
    C -->|OUT_OF_SCOPE| Z1[Return block message]
    C -->|NEEDS CLARIFICATION| Z2[Return clarification question]
    C -->|READY_FOR_SQL| D[SQLAgent.generate_sql]

    D --> E[validate_sql]
    E -->|invalid| F[ErrorAgent.repair_sql]
    E -->|valid| G[execute_sql]

    G -->|execution error| F
    F --> H{Retry count < max?}
    H -->|yes| E
    H -->|no| Z3[Return error recovery failure]

    G -->|success| I[format_response]
    I --> J[AnalysisAgent.summarize]
    J --> K[VizAgent.generate\n(fallback: infer_plotly)]
    K --> L[Return final payload]
